android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYS.description: Allows the application to mount and unmount file systems for removable storage.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.PACKAGE_USAGE_STATS.description: Allows the modification of collected component usage statistics. Not for use by common applications.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.SET_WALLPAPER.description: Allows the application to set the system wallpaper.

playstore_details.title: Photo Collage Maker - Collage Editor, Photo Pro
playstore_details.description:
With Photo Collage Maker, you can cut and resize your photo. You can combine different photo as your like. Various of photo posture demonstration, easy to get new photo. Photo Collage Maker has photo edit tools. Edit your pictures as you wish. You can show your perfect photo share your beauty with your friends for free.

The Main Function:

Photo pose guide and you'll be able to easily get fashion style photos
More than 100+ collage layouts for you to combine your photos
Remix up to 9 photos to create interesting layouts and template
Freestyle to collage your photo
Edit every photo with colorful effects
Background with a gradient color makes your image more distinctive
Unique photo effects make photo collages
Using frame effects to make it even more unique
Add Emoji stickers in your photo
Powerful photo tool and one-click to change photo style

How to use:

Photo pose guide
50+ photo posture demonstration. With different themes, you can find poses that fit different scenes.

Photo Edit Tool
Slim and Full
Adjust Eyes, Nose, Mouth on face
Stretch Legs easily

Colorful Filter
100+ Different filter scenes for food, scenery, people, pets etc.
Take a photo by our amazing filter, make your photos to be beautiful, and share on your SNS.

 60+ Stickers
Various of stickers, you can choose one or more stickers which you like to add on your photos.
With new emoji cartoon stickers, it's easy to edit funny pic.
What’s more, there are many funny motion stickers face filters and neon stickers are waiting for you.

Theme Poster
A large number of freestyle templates
Edit your photo collage more different

Contact Us 
Photo Collage Maker offers Fashion Freestyle and 60+ stickers.
Please contact us If you have some suggestions or ideas.
Mail: lingz3731@gmail.com
